name: Cook Master
description:
You need to collect the good treats and dodge the non-food. 

It will be a mobile game if released but for now I'm keeping it as a browser game, instead of sliding your finger you need to just move your mouse!

This is a small hobby project and I don't know if I will finish it, but if you have any ideas on how to make it more fun or add anything let me know in the comments!
